You can save stops and addresses under favorites to make it even easier for you to get around Hamburg. Your most frequently entered destinations also appear automatically on your hvv homescreen, saving you time and making it even easier to start your journey. 

DEPARTURES NEAR YOU 
You know where to go? We show you when! The hvv app shows you the departures of all lines of nearby stops in your area. So you quickly know when to get on and save yourself the hassle of searching for connections. Keep the best overview of your public transport everywhere with your hvv app and always get to your desired destination quickly. 

DISRUPTION MESSAGES 
With your hvv app you always stay up to date. Under "messages" all messages on your favorite lines are clearly displayed. Whether construction work, road closures, or cancellations. You are prepared for every situation. 

ALSO INTERESTING 
For even more flexibility: test the offer of hvv switch and book MOIA, MILES, SIXT share and TIER in one app.
